description: This file serves as the entry point for a React application. It imports core React libraries, CSS styles, and the main App component. It initializes the React root and renders the App component inside StrictMode for additional checks.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot

methods.description: Renders React elements into the root managed by ReactDOM.
